App Launcher Drew N. Edition for Microsoft Office 2010 ProPlus Version 2.4, Update 2 Compiled for 32-bit systems with a 32-bit installation of Office 2010
Made by Drew Naylor This app allows you to get to your favorite Office 2010 ProPlus application very quickly. It can also clear up space on your desktop. I am not intending on infringing on Microsoft's copyrights, so this is only a shortcut application.
App compiled on Saturday, December 7, 2013
